reviewText: Early Access Review\n\nI like the feel of this game. Your strategy build with each run at defending the Earth it is fast paced and you really have to use timing to upgrade and have a build strategy in mind before setting out. Very interested in what the final product will be like, lots of potential and great fun.

reviewText: Early Access Review\n\nThis game seems to be very good balanced and nice to play even at early access stage already at that point. Good combination of strategy and action involved with simple earth alien confrontation defense survival basis. Good job !!
